    <field name="description">
      <value>It would be helpful if Castle.Tools.CodeGenerator.CmdLine supported an AdditionalReferencePath argument, which would make the tool work when running msbuild from the command line like so:

msbuild /p:OutputPath=${build.dir} solution.sln

Right now, the generator only checks the output paths of the csproj, which fails when running msbuild like above. Supporting 'Castle.Tools.CodeGenerator.CmdLine /AdditionalReferencePath:${build.dir}' fixes this.
</value>
